  "title": "Lorry Crane Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong><br>\nThe Lorry Crane Driver is a driver and operator of Lorry crane. Performs ad hoc duties as<br>\nand when required and maintain company’s vehicle.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong><br>\nUnderstand and comply with safety requirements.</p>\n<p>Follow Singapore traffic regulations.</p>\n<p>Drive the Lorry and also Operate the Lorry Crane Transport materials and equipment.</p>\n<p>Perform safe lifting operation at various site as required.</p>\n<p>Perform maintenance on vehicles such as cleaning interior and exterior &amp; report immediately if any defects.</p>\n<p>Planning routes and travel schedules to ensure timely delivery of goods and diesel dispense.</p>\n<p>Conducting vehicle maintenance checks to ensure that trucks are in good operating condition.</p>\n<p>Loading and unloading freight using appropriate tools and equipment.</p>\n<p>Keeping accurate records of trucking activities, including mileage and fuel consumption.</p>\n<p>Must follow common safety regulations at Plant &amp; Site.</p>\n<p>Fetch workers to construction site (as and when required)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements &amp; Professional Skills</strong><br>\nMinimum Primary Education<br>\nAble to communicate in basic English / Mandarin<br>\nShould Possess valid Class 4 / Class 5 Singapore Driving Experience<br>\nShould Possess WSQ certificate in Lorry Crane Operation or Equivalent<br>\nPhysically fit, Self-disciplined, responsible, punctual, reliable<br>\nMinimum (2) years driving experience in Singapore is required<br>\nMinimum (1) year experience in operating Lorry Crane<br>\nGood familiarity with Singapore roads and traffic pattern is required.<br>\nShould have some minimal knowledge on Vehicle Maintenance</p>",
